<p>The best hairball remedies do more than help hair slide through your cat’s body. They treat the problem at its root by supporting overall digestive health.</p>
<p>That’s why we chose Cat Lax as the best hairball remedy on the market. This well known hairball gel contains a blend of ingredients that break up hairballs, prevent new ones from forming, and minimize shedding to keep hairballs at bay.</p>
